dcterms:description: A time series dataset containing price data for various cryptocurrencies traded on the Binance exchange, spanning from 2018-06-10 to 2023-06-04, covering 12 currencies priced in USDT including ADA, BNB, BTC, EOS, ETH, IOTA, LTC, NEO, ONT, QTUM, XLM, and XRP.
dcterms:title: Binance Price Time Series

dcterms:description: A time series dataset containing price data for various cryptocurrencies traded on the Coinbase exchange, spanning from 2019-08-08 to 2023-08-17, covering 10 currencies priced in USD including BCH, BTC, EOS, ETC, ETH, LINK, LTC, XLM, XTZ, and ZRX.
dcterms:title: Coinbase Price Time Series

dcterms:description: A dataset containing historical asset returns used for fitting generative models in portfolio construction.
dcterms:title: Historical Asset Returns

dcterms:description: Data generated from multivariate Gaussian and Student’s t distributions used for modeling asset returns.
dcterms:title: Multivariate Gaussian and Student’s t Distributions

dcterms:description: Data used for fitting the DCC-GARCH model, which captures the volatility clustering and time-varying correlations of asset returns.
dcterms:title: DCC-GARCH Model Data

dcterms:description: Data generated from vine copula models used for modeling multivariate dependencies in asset returns.
dcterms:title: Vine Copula Data

dcterms:description: Historical returns data used for fitting generative models in portfolio construction.
dcterms:title: Historical Returns for Generative Model Fitting
